<plot>Nobel Prize-winning scientist 'Nurse, Sir Paul' (qv) presents in this documentary what could be the future in the war against cancer. Starting with the advances in chemo-therapy that helps large numbers of children overcome their cancers. Finishing with the first human trials of new experimental cancer drugs that specifically target cancer cells leading many scientists to believe that they could be on the verge of treating a great many varieties of cancer in this new way.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?351773</url></doc>
